        <abstract>
            <p>Praises MT’s observations and asks her to repeat experiments on the the relation of sexes of butterflies to the nutrition of the larvae.</p> 
<p>Is glad she will publish her observations on <hi rend="italic">Drosera</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
